ever did set a skb->dst entry earlier than bridge in those days."

Fixes: 1da177e4c3f4 ("Linux-2.6.12-rc2")
Signed-off-by: Harsh Modi <harshmodi@google.com>
Acked-by: Florian Westphal <fw@strlen.de>
